ReferenceDocuments.name: Case Report Form
ReferenceDocuments.description: Record the name of the reproductive system finding if not pre-printed on the CRF. If collected on the CRF, the sponsor may provide additional instructions to ensure the data is entered as intended.

ReferenceDocuments.name: RPTEST; RPTESTCD
ReferenceDocuments.description: Maps directly to the SDTMIG variable. The SDTMIG variable RPTESTCD may be determined from the value collected in RPTEST. The SDTMIG variables RPTESTCD and RPTEST are required in the SDTM submission datasets. Use appropriate CDISC Controlled Terminology for the test and test code.

ReferenceDocuments.name: CDASH Implementation Notes
ReferenceDocuments.description: Required to identify which test the result is for. It is recommended that the test names be pre-printed on the CRF rather than collected in a field that requires the site to enter text. If the form is laid out as a grid, then words such as Test can be included as the column header.
